msgid "Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, appassutassa bāhusaccakathā dukkathā? "
msgstr "And why is it inappropriate to talk to an unlearned person about learning? "

msgctxt "an5.157:4.2"
msgid "Appassuto, bhikkhave, bāhusaccakathāya kacchamānāya abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
