msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an5.157:4.4"
msgid "Tañhi so, bhikkhave, sutasampadaṃ attani na samanupassati, na ca labhati tatonidānaṃ pītipāmojjaṃ. "
