msgstr "That’s why it’s inappropriate to talk to an unlearned person about learning. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.182, sc5
msgctxt "an5.157:5.1"
msgid "Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, maccharissa cāgakathā dukkathā? "
msgstr "And why is it inappropriate to talk to a stingy person about generosity? "

msgctxt "an5.157:5.2"
msgid "Maccharī, bhikkhave, cāgakathāya kacchamānāya abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
