msgctxt "an5.157:5.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "an5.157:5.4"
msgid "Tañhi so, bhikkhave, cāgasampadaṃ attani na samanupassati na ca labhati tatonidānaṃ pītipāmojjaṃ. "
msgstr "Not seeing that generosity in themselves, they don’t get the rapture and joy that generosity brings. "

msgctxt "an5.157:5.5"
msgid "Tasmā maccharissa cāgakathā dukkathā. "
msgstr "That’s why it’s inappropriate to talk to a stingy person about generosity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an5.157:6.1"
msgid "Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, duppaññassa paññākathā dukkathā? "
msgstr "And why is it inappropriate to talk to a witless person about wisdom? "

msgctxt "an5.157:6.2"
msgid "Duppañño, bhikkhave, paññākathāya kacchamānāya abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
