msgid "Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, cāgavato cāgakathā sukathā? "
msgstr "And why is it appropriate to talk to a generous person about generosity? "

msgctxt "an5.157:11.2"
msgid "Cāgavā, bhikkhave, cāgakathāya kacchamānāya nābhisajjati na kuppati na byāpajjati na patitthīyati na kopañca dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti. "
