msgstr "Seeing that generosity in themselves, they get the rapture and joy that generosity brings. "

msgctxt "an5.157:11.5"
msgid "Tasmā cāgavato cāgakathā sukathā. "
msgstr "That’s why it’s appropriate to talk to a generous person about generosity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "an5.157:12.1"
msgid "Kasmā ca, bhikkhave, paññavato paññākathā sukathā? "
msgstr "And why is it appropriate to talk to a wise person about wisdom? "

