msgid "Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, pañcannaṃ puggalānaṃ kathā sukathā puggale puggalaṃ upanidhāyā”ti. "
msgstr "These are topics that are appropriate to talk about, taking into consideration which specific one of five people you are talking to.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
